title: QGIS Australia Community Hackathon
content: We're excited to invite everyone to QGIS Australia's second "Community Hackathon" on November 4th, where we will explore a range of tasks to further the QGIS project. This event is open to everyone wanting to contribute to QGIS, not just developers or those already involved in the project! If you've ever wanted to dive into the QGIS community and find out how you can help, then this event is perfect for you... Double-click this entry to learn more.
